Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Baybay Elementary School in the Municipality of San Jose, Province of Antique, to Governor Santos Capadocia Memorial School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 330
An Act Changing the Name of the Baybay Elementary School in the Municipality of San Jose, Province of Antique, to Governor Santos Capadocia Memorial School
Section 1. The name of the Baybay Elementary School in the Municipality of San Jose, Province of Antique, is changed to Governor Santos Capadocia Memorial School.1awp++i1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: January 19, 1983
